— Registered as Commodity Pool Operator and Commodity Trading Adviser with the CFTC
— Responsible for portfolio supervision and asset evaluation


Olden Lane Securities LLC Broker-Dealer, Member FINRA / SIPC
— Sponsor and Underwriter of Olden Lane Trust, a unit investment trust platform
— Coordinates distribution and marketing of Olden Lane products
